{{Use British English|date=October 2018}} {{Use mdy dates|date=October 2018}} {{Infobox television | show_name = Rabbids Invasion | image = Rabbids Invasion logo.svg | genre = {{Unbulleted list|[[Comedy]]|[[Slapstick]]}} | creator = [[Ubisoft]] | writer = | director = {{Unbulleted list|Akama|Fabien Ouvrard|Stéphane Mit|Franz Kirchner}} | developer = [[Ubisoft Motion Pictures]] | voices = Damien Laquet | narrated = | theme_music_composer = | opentheme = | composer = Le Belle Equipe | country = {{Unbulleted list|United States|France}} | language = {{Unbulleted list|English|French}} | num_seasons = 3 | num_episodes = 78 (229 segments) | list_episodes = List of Rabbids Invasion episodes | executive_producer = {{Unbulleted list|Jean-Julien Baronnet {{small|(season 1–3)}}|Didier Lupfer {{small|(season 2)}}}} | producer = {{Unbulleted list|Frédéric Thonet {{small|(season 1–3)}}|Fannie Pailloux {{small|(season 1–3)}}|Damien Leyris {{small|(season 2)}}|Ruben Berissi {{small|(season 3)}}}} | editor = | story_editor = | camera = | runtime = ~24 minutes (3 7-minute segments) | company = {{Unbulleted list|[[Ubisoft Motion Pictures]]|[[TeamTO]]}} | network = [[France 3]] | picture_format = 1080i | audio_format = Stereo | first_aired = {{Start date|2013|8|3}} | last_aired = present }}
'''''Rabbids Invasion''''' ({{lang-fr|Les Lapins Crétins : Invasion}}) is an [[animated television series]] that premiered on August 3, 2013, on [[France 3]]. The series was a French-American co-production from [[Ubisoft Motion Pictures]], [[TeamTO]], [[France Télévisions]] and [[Nickelodeon Productions]]. The show is based on the ''[[Raving Rabbids]]'' video game series produced by [[Ubisoft]]. Three seasons, each with 26 episodes, aired between 2013 and 2017. A fourth season is airing on France 3, and will be available worldwide through [[Netflix]], as well as in China through [[iQiyi]].<ref>https://variety.com/2018/film/news/rabbids-invasion-renewed-1202974477/</ref>
==Cast== * Damien Laquet as the Rabbids
